# PM2 Restart Reminder

When making many changes in one session, periodically restart PM2 services before validating tests or reporting status.

- Use exact process names: `litreview-api`, `litreview-ui`, `litreview-tunnel`.
- After backend `src/` changes: run `pm2 restart litreview-api`.
- After frontend changes that must reflect on production URL: run `cd frontend && pnpm build && cd ..` then `pm2 restart litreview-api`.
- Before claiming local/online verification, run `pm2 list` and confirm required processes are online.
